for the Book in the Library

00:00:36.630 --> 00:00:42.820
of Congress an organization was
created by Dr. Daniel Boorstin back

00:00:42.820 --> 00:00:48.270
in 1977 to reach out on behalf
of the Library of Congress

00:00:48.270 --> 00:00:52.790
to promote books and reading
