waiting rooms.

00:59:01.830 --> 00:59:03.890
In the best situation,
we have volunteers

00:59:03.890 --> 00:59:05.710
who are reading with the children.

00:59:05.710 --> 00:59:10.220
And more importantly, demonstrating
to the parents two things,

00:59:10.220 --> 00:59:14.130
