wait for an hour for their visits.

00:59:28.370 --> 00:59:32.940 position:56%
So instead of that hour being filled
with the kind of control speech

00:59:32.940 --> 00:59:35.450
that you talked about,
it was an hour now filled

00:59:35.450 --> 00:59:40.970
with observing their children
responding to books and somebody

00:59:40.970 --> 00:59:42.970
who could present them
in a happy way.

00:59:42.970 --> 00:59:47.140
And we discovered a form of
waiting room contagion which was

00:59:47.140 --> 00:59:51.210
that as parents were watching one
person interacting with children

00:59:51.210 --> 00:59:53.720
about books, other
kids would come along

00:59:53.720 --> 00:59:56.120
and then the parents would hang
in the back would start picking

00:59:56.120 --> 00:59:58.350
up the books and looking at
them with their children.

00:59:58.350 --> 01:00:01.410
So pretty soon we created a milieu

01:00:01.410 --> 01:00:03.820
