only takes about one

01:28:02.170 --> 01:28:03.680
to two years to learn to read.

01:28:03.680 --> 01:28:06.370
If you're Chinese it
takes about 10 years.

01:28:06.370 --> 01:28:10.420
So it definitely varies
depending on the complexity

01:28:10.420 --> 01:28:12.720
of the written language system.

01:28:12.720 --> 01:28:16.650
