02:45:13.750 --> 02:45:16.650
or 8 p.m. Restaurants
were not supposed

02:45:16.650 --> 02:45:18.850
to be open unless you were a hotel

02:45:18.850 --> 02:45:22.080
and therefore you needed
to feed your guest.

02:45:22.080 --> 02:45:26.240
Traditional burial practices
were eventually outlawed

02:45:26.240 --> 02:45:30.220 position:56%
