02:49:34.840 --> 02:49:38.660
And two was to communicate
the message about Ebola.

02:49:38.660 --> 02:49:41.860
And this I think was the
most affective way to do it.

02:49:41.860 --> 02:49:45.130
It was a lot of manpower
and it was drastic.

02:49:45.130 --> 02:49:46.830
But it seemed to then work

02:49:46.830 --> 02:49:50.030
because the numbers began
to go down after that.

02:49:50.030 --> 02:49:52.630
There was diligent contact tracing.

02:49:52.630 --> 02:49:57.050
