02:52:03.180 --> 02:52:05.150
So we used social mobilization.

02:52:05.150 --> 02:52:08.760
And if a community felt that school
was not cleaned it was not open,

02:52:08.760 --> 02:52:11.070
they would report it
back to the ministry

02:52:11.070 --> 02:52:16.870
and then we would engage the-- so
the Ministry of Health to make sure

02:52:16.870 --> 02:52:18.800
that it gets cleaned
because the Ministry

02:52:18.800 --> 02:52:22.390
of Health took care of
cleaning the schools.

02:52:22.390 --> 02:52:26.670
We also used the radio to inform
parents that schools are safe

02:52:26.670 --> 02:52:30.830
to reopen that they are
being sanitized the--

02:52:30.830 --> 02:52:34.270
