be ensured safety

02:52:34.270 --> 02:52:35.850
that there are measures in place.

02:52:35.850 --> 02:52:38.770
And then we trained at
least one teacher per school

02:52:38.770 --> 02:52:44.090
to understand how to
deal with Ebola.

02:52:44.090 --> 02:52:48.410
The reason I wanted to put to
say that we covered psychosocial

02:52:48.410 --> 02:52:52.970
and technical areas is we wanted to
make sure that if a child is found

02:52:52.970 --> 02:52:57.070 position:56%
